  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个事件驱动架构的时序图，核心流程是：Aggregate产生事件存入Event Store，然后有个Reactor监听并推送任务到Queue，最后Worker去执行具体的Side Effect。关键是成功和失败要有不同的处理分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，我梳理一下参与者顺序：Aggregate → Event Store → Reactor → Queue → Queue Worker → Side Effect。关于分支，成功时Worker要标记任务完成，失败时要重试，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect",
        "Mark Job as Completed",
        "Retry Job"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，但注意重试是Worker通知Queue去重试，不是Worker自己直接重试。还有，Reactor到Queue是Push Job，不是简单的调用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Push Job",
        "Retry Job"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先画出主流程：Aggregate向Event Store发送Store Event，Event Store向Reactor分发Dispatch Event，Reactor推送Push Job到Queue，Queue让Worker去Process Job，最后Worker执行Execute Side Effect。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect",
        "Store Event",
        "Dispatch Event",
        "Push Job",
        "Process Job",
        "Execute Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "主流程没问题，现在加上alt分支。成功路径：Side Effect返回成功，Worker通知Queue标记任务完成。失败路径：返回失败，Worker通知Queue重试任务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Side Effect",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue",
        "Return Success",
        "Mark Job as Completed",
        "Return Failure",
        "Retry Job"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加alt块，Success分支是S-W返回成功、W-Q标记完成；Failure分支是S-W返回失败、W-Q重试任务。整体用dark主题，配色按深灰系调整。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Side Effect",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue",
        "Return Success",
        "Mark Job as Completed",
        "Return Failure",
        "Retry Job"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Worker到Side Effect的箭头方向画反了，应该是Worker调用Side Effect，不是Side Effect主动指向Worker。还有，Store Event和Dispatch Event的箭头也要确认是从左到右。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect",
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Execute Side Effect",
        "Store Event",
        "Dispatch Event"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "已修正，现在所有箭头方向正确：Aggregate→Event Store→Reactor→Queue→Worker→Side Effect，返回消息也是双向正确。alt分支的两种结果都清晰了，图可以定稿。",
